00:12:11.630 --> 00:12:14.730 align:middle line:84%
the catalyzers, the
enzymatic process,

00:12:14.730 --> 00:12:17.730 align:middle line:84%
are dependent on things
like minerals and vitamins

00:12:17.730 --> 00:12:22.290 align:middle line:84%
and amino acids of
certain branches.

00:12:22.290 --> 00:12:26.700 align:middle line:84%
And this is what we need to
be educating our patients on.

00:12:26.700 --> 00:12:29.400 align:middle line:84%
