00:12:38.190 --> 00:12:40.770 align:middle line:84%
got their own individual taste
when it comes to veganism

00:12:40.770 --> 00:12:41.880 align:middle line:90%
or if there's animal.

00:12:41.880 --> 00:12:43.890 align:middle line:84%
I have meat about two,
three times a week,

00:12:43.890 --> 00:12:45.060 align:middle line:90%
but that works for me.

00:12:45.060 --> 00:12:47.730 align:middle line:84%
