00:13:26.790 --> 00:13:29.370 align:middle line:84%
So your circadian rhythms
are really, really important

00:13:29.370 --> 00:13:32.490 align:middle line:84%
when it comes to eating
because that determines--

00:13:32.490 --> 00:13:34.650 align:middle line:84%
when you eat, it determines
your circadian rhythm.

00:13:34.650 --> 00:13:36.690 align:middle line:84%
That has an effect on
melatonin, all these

00:13:36.690 --> 00:13:39.120 align:middle line:84%
