hydrating ourselves,

00:13:46.680 --> 00:13:48.280 align:middle line:84%
and there is a
focus on making sure

00:13:48.280 --> 00:13:49.650 align:middle line:90%
that we're having enough water.

00:13:49.650 --> 00:13:51.390 align:middle line:84%
There is a balance,
under hydration

00:13:51.390 --> 00:13:52.710 align:middle line:90%
versus over hydration.

00:13:52.710 --> 00:13:54.752 align:middle line:84%
