00:14:47.140 --> 00:14:50.160 align:middle line:84%
So those are the basic
principles-- colorful bowls,

00:14:50.160 --> 00:14:53.860 align:middle line:84%
hydration, good quality fats,
and good quality proteins

00:14:53.860 --> 00:14:54.660 align:middle line:90%
as well.

